{
  "id": "RAW_846c1c",
  "title": "月之暗面「调教」出最强 Agent，在「人类最后一场考试」拿下最新 SOTA ｜ 机器之心",
  "url": "https://www.jiqizhixin.com/articles/2025-06-21-7",
  "date": "2025-06-21 13:31:40",
  "author": "机器之心",
  "siteName": "机器之心",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>昨天，月之暗面发了篇博客，介绍了一款名为 Kimi-Researcher 的自主 Agent。</p>\n  <p>这款 Agent 擅长多轮搜索和推理，平均每项任务执行 23 个推理步骤，访问超过 200 个网址。它是基于 Kimi k 系列模型的内部版本构建，并完全通过端到端智能体强化学习进行训练，也是国内少有的基于自研模型打造的 Agent。</p>\n  <p><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/eee3ef04-b437-4b36-0557-d37148825900/public\" alt=\"image.png\" data-ratio=\"0.3\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"503491461\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"1\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/b510f62c-9463-4de9-b337-89a269186919/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"0\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\"></p>\n  <p>GitHub 链接：https://moonshotai.github.io/Kimi-Researcher/</p>\n  <p>在「人类最后一场考试」(Humanity's Last Exam) 中，Kimi-Researcher 取得了 26.9% 的 Pass@1 成绩，创下最新的 SOTA 水平，Pass@4 准确率也达到了 40.17%。</p>\n  <p>从初始的 8.6% HLE 分数开始，Kimi-Researcher 几乎完全依靠端到端的强化学习训练将成绩提升至 26.9%，强有力地证明了端到端智能体强化学习在提升 Agent 智能方面的巨大潜力。</p>\n  <p>Kimi-Researcher 还在多个复杂且极具挑战性的实际基准测试中表现出色。在 xbench （一款旨在将 AI 能力与实际生产力相结合的全新动态、专业对齐套件）上，Kimi-Researcher 在 xbench-DeepSearch 子任务上平均 pass@1 达到了 69% 的分数（4 次运行的平均值），超越了诸如 o3 等带有搜索工具的模型。在多轮搜索推理（如 FRAMES、Seal-0）和事实信息检索（如 SimpleQA）等基准测试中，Kimi-Researcher 同样取得了优异成绩。</p>\n  <p><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/005e6f1e-0680-458f-39e9-77d892db2600/public\" alt=\"image.png\" data-ratio=\"0.8064814814814815\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"503491462\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"2\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/fb404ad0-8aeb-4c7b-98da-3c1026d1af3c/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"1\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\"></p>\n  <p>举个例子。我们想找一部外国动画电影，但只记得大概剧情：</p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <section data-id=\"119086\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\">\n    <section>\n     <section>\n      <section data-width=\"100%\">\n       <section>\n        <section>\n         <section data-width=\"100%\">\n          <section>\n           <section data-autoskip=\"1\">\n            <section data-ace-gallery-json=\"{&quot;items&quot;:[{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;625c6096-3698-4cc5-a73c-dfc6cae6f70b&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:1320,&quot;width&quot;:2658,&quot;currHeight&quot;:1320,&quot;currWidth&quot;:2658,&quot;natrualHeight&quot;:1320,&quot;natrualWidth&quot;:2658,&quot;pluginName&quot;:&quot;imageUpload&quot;,&quot;scale&quot;:1,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https%3A%2F%2Finternal-api-drive-stream.feishu.cn%2Fspace%2Fapi%2Fbox%2Fstream%2Fdownload%2Fpreview%2FHt9ubFPYaofqCzxDXgQcWhr0nIe%2F%3Fpreview_type%3D16&quot;,&quot;file_token&quot;:&quot;Ht9ubFPYaofqCzxDXgQcWhr0nIe&quot;,&quot;image_type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:1227199,&quot;comments&quot;:[]}]}\" data-type=\"image\">\n             <section data-ace-gallery-json=\"{&quot;items&quot;:[{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;4e575bca-e566-4a46-9385-50da6853a9ea&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:1026,&quot;width&quot;:1872,&quot;currHeight&quot;:1026,&quot;currWidth&quot;:1872,&quot;natrualHeight&quot;:1026,&quot;natrualWidth&quot;:1872,&quot;pluginName&quot;:&quot;imageUpload&quot;,&quot;scale&quot;:1,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https%3A%2F%2Finternal-api-drive-stream.feishu.cn%2Fspace%2Fapi%2Fbox%2Fstream%2Fdownload%2Fpreview%2FKRI7bimjcom5BSxojGPcUg1Snhb%2F%3Fpreview_type%3D16&quot;,&quot;file_token&quot;:&quot;KRI7bimjcom5BSxojGPcUg1Snhb&quot;,&quot;image_type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:967207,&quot;comments&quot;:[]}]}\" data-type=\"image\">\n              <section>\n               <section>\n                <section data-ace-gallery-json=\"{&quot;items&quot;:[{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;8e2abeb7-211c-44c8-b443-8e11c26cf890&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:1406,&quot;width&quot;:898,&quot;currHeight&quot;:1406,&quot;currWidth&quot;:898,&quot;natrualHeight&quot;:1406,&quot;natrualWidth&quot;:898,&quot;pluginName&quot;:&quot;imageUpload&quot;,&quot;scale&quot;:1,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https%3A%2F%2Finternal-api-drive-stream.feishu.cn%2Fspace%2Fapi%2Fbox%2Fstream%2Fdownload%2Fpreview%2FQlLibj2MJo57BcxJgMJcT8lRnyf%2F%3Fpreview_type%3D16&quot;,&quot;file_token&quot;:&quot;QlLibj2MJo57BcxJgMJcT8lRnyf&quot;,&quot;image_type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:198357,&quot;comments&quot;:[]}]}\" data-type=\"image\">\n                 <section data-ace-gallery-json=\"{&quot;items&quot;:[{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;00725e6f-28d1-4211-a634-b089afc0759f&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:1400,&quot;width&quot;:1494,&quot;currHeight&quot;:1400,&quot;currWidth&quot;:1494,&quot;natrualHeight&quot;:1400,&quot;natrualWidth&quot;:1494,&quot;pluginName&quot;:&quot;imageUpload&quot;,&quot;scale&quot;:1,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https%3A%2F%2Finternal-api-drive-stream.feishu.cn%2Fspace%2Fapi%2Fbox%2Fstream%2Fdownload%2Fpreview%2FJKqib2bZ5og1NUxCUqwczfyTnHg%2F%3Fpreview_type%3D16&quot;,&quot;file_token&quot;:&quot;JKqib2bZ5og1NUxCUqwczfyTnHg&quot;,&quot;image_type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:291311,&quot;comments&quot;:[]}]}\" data-type=\"image\">\n                  <section>\n                   <section>\n                    <section data-ace-gallery-json=\"{&quot;items&quot;:[{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;7254af1d-28ce-4c35-9c34-3f6d3bf71033&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:3255,&quot;width&quot;:1149,&quot;currHeight&quot;:3255,&quot;currWidth&quot;:1149,&quot;natrualHeight&quot;:3255,&quot;natrualWidth&quot;:1149,&quot;pluginName&quot;:&quot;imageUpload&quot;,&quot;scale&quot;:1,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https%3A%2F%2Finternal-api-drive-stream.feishu.cn%2Fspace%2Fapi%2Fbox%2Fstream%2Fdownload%2Fpreview%2FSrnPbmnKyopOIjxViUmcvYz9nia%2F%3Fpreview_type%3D16&quot;,&quot;file_token&quot;:&quot;SrnPbmnKyopOIjxViUmcvYz9nia&quot;,&quot;image_type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:338706,&quot;comments&quot;:[]}]}\" data-type=\"image\">\n                     <section>\n                      <section>\n                       <section data-ace-gallery-json=\"{&quot;items&quot;:[{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;dfb75b45-d2cb-47